    "tagline": "An AI agent that lives in this repository — powered by the <a class=\"link\" href=\"https://github.com/japer-technology/github-minimum-intelligence\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">GitHub Minimum Intelligence</a> framework. Every conversation, every action, every line of code is committed here — versioned, auditable, and visible to anyone.",
