              "html": "Other supported providers include OpenAI, Google Gemini, xAI, DeepSeek, Mistral, Groq, and OpenRouter. See the <a class=\"link\" href=\"https://github.com/japer-technology/github-minimum-intelligence\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">framework documentation</a> for details.",
